1.2
log
@* games went off to ports/games/bsdgames
* don't install isakmpd or ctm samples
@
text
@/*	$OpenBSD: grammar.y,v 1.3 1999/07/31 20:08:29 pjanzen Exp $	*/
/*	$NetBSD: grammar.y,v 1.3 1995/03/21 15:03:59 cgd Exp $	*/

